{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-chenfeng-006__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-chenfeng-006", "source_id": "guofeng-chenfeng-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·陳風·006.1", "text_original": "墓門有棘，斧以斯之。夫也不良，國人知之。知而不已，誰昔然矣。", "text_normalized": "墓門有棘，斧以斯之。夫也不良，國人知之。知而不已，誰昔然矣。", "notes": "墓門 Chinese stanza 1."}
